heading: 2. The 29th day of December 2023 is appointed as the day on which
text_raw:
2. The 29th day of December 2023 is appointed as the day on which 
sections 3, 4, 5, 6, and 10 of the Central Bank (Individual Accountability 
Framework) Act 2023 (No. 5 of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

27 June, 2023. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 7th July, 2023.
